{"id":75241,"title":"[A storyteller in gerontology].","abstract":"Storytelling in geriatrics is a way of contributing to the construction of an alternative to the pharmacological treatment of cognitive disorders. To carry out such an activity, aside from having a repertoire of targeted stories and the talent of a good storyteller, it is important to know how to create a convivial atmosphere where the patient will feel appreciated and valued.","date":"2014-08-20","categories":"Nervous System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25137968","annotations":[{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.841915,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Pharmacology","weight":0.804197,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pharmacology"},{"name":"Cognition","weight":0.708098,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cognition"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.669249,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Geriatrics","weight":0.639828,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geriatrics"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.524967,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Construction","weight":0.136736,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Construction"},{"name":"Gerontology","weight":0.0388889,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gerontology"},{"name":"Atmosphere","weight":0.0377168,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atmosphere"},{"name":"Symposium","weight":0.0332387,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Symposium"},{"name":"Storytelling","weight":0.023431,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Storytelling"},{"name":"Songwriter","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Songwriter"},{"name":"Alternative rock","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alternative_rock"},{"name":"Skill","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.